<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<base href="/">
<title>Stripe Payment Admin</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap-theme.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/application.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/adduser.css">
<script src="js/jquery-1.12.4.min.js"></script>
<script src="js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container main hidden">
        <div class="row header">
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-xs-12 col-sm-offset-3">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <h1 class="boldi light-blue">Ipefix Payment Solution</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row content">
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-xs-12 border-right">
                <div class="content-left">
                    <h2 class="dark-blue boldi">Nouvel utilisateur</h2>
                    <form action="{{ path_for('newclient') }}" method="post">
                        <input type="hidden" name="{{csrf.keys.name}}" value="{{csrf.name}}">
                        <input type="hidden" name="{{csrf.keys.value}}" value="{{csrf.value}}">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="name" placeholder="Domaine" required>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" name="email" placeholder="Email" required>
                            <input type="password" class="form-control" name="pwd" placeholder="Password" required>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default btn-sm btn-block bold">Ajouter</button>
                            <div class="checkbox">
                                <label>
                                    <input name="cg-ok" type="checkbox" value="1" required>
                                    J'ai lu et j'accepte les conditions d'utilisation du service.
                                </label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-xs-12 border-left">
                <div class="content-right">
                    <p>
                        Veuillez indiquer votre nom, 
                        une adresse e-mail de contact et 
                        un mot de passe. Ce dernier devra 
                        se composer d'un minimum de 8 caract√®res.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row footer">
            <div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-4">
                <div class="text-center copyr">&copy; Ipefix 2019</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container loader"></div>
    <script src="js/loadingoverlay.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/application.js"></script>
</body>
</html>